  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要为Education ContentCDN设计一个状态流转图，核心服务是Education_ClassroomService。整体流程从IDLE开始，通过Kick-off触发FETCH操作。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Education_ClassroomService",
        "IDLE",
        "FETCH",
        "Kick-off"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白了，起点是IDLE，触发条件是Kick-off。FETCH完成后进入PARSE状态对吗？那PARSE之后应该有两个分支吧？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "FETCH",
        "PARSE"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，PARSE要判断数据有效性。Valid的话走ARB_READ申请读权限，Invalid则进入ERROR状态。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "PARSE",
        "ARB_READ",
        "ERROR",
        "Valid",
        "Invalid"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我先把主干画出来：IDLE→FETCH→PARSE，然后PARSE分出两条线。接下来ARB_READ之后呢？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "IDLE",
        "FETCH",
        "PARSE",
        "ARB_READ",
        "ERROR"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "ARB_READ获得Grant后进入READ，READ完成后到ARB_WRITE申请写权限，Grant之后进入WRITE。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "ARB_READ",
        "READ",
        "Grant",
        "ARB_WRITE",
        "WRITE"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "这里有个问题——WRITE完成后应该回到FETCH继续处理下一条，还是直接结束？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "WRITE",
        "FETCH"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "WRITE完成后先到CHAIN状态，由CHAIN判断：如果是Next就回到FETCH，如果是Last就进入COMPLETE。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "WRITE",
        "CHAIN",
        "FETCH",
        "COMPLETE",
        "Next",
        "Last"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "清楚了，COMPLETE之后通过IRQ sent回到IDLE。那ERROR状态呢，怎么恢复？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "COMPLETE",
        "IDLE",
        "IRQ sent",
        "ERROR"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 9,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "ERROR通过SW clear软件清除后回到IDLE。这样整个闭环就完成了。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "ERROR",
        "IDLE",
        "SW clear"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 10,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，最终状态图已确认：从Education_ClassroomService进入IDLE，经过FETCH-PARSE-ARB_READ-READ-ARB_WRITE-WRITE-CHAIN的完整链路，支持循环处理和异常恢复。",
